GtkTetcolor 0.6.4   (May 25 2004)
=================
 o fixed compilation by gcc-3.4
 o updated intltool version which fixes configuring without OrigTree 
   perl module
 o fixed loading of a current font into fontselection widget in the preferences 
   dialog

GtkTetcolor 0.6.3   (Mar 25 2004)
=================
 o ported to Gtk+-2.4

GtkTetcolor 0.6.2   (Mar 12 2003)
=================
 o added experimental rpm-spec-file
 o German translation

GtkTetcolor 0.6.1   (Dec 19 2002)
=================
 o ported to win32
 o minor bug and portability fixes

GtkTetcolor 0.6.0   (Nov 21 2002)
=================
 o fixed memory leak in changing of font
 o code was cleaned up

GtkTetcolor 0.6.0pre1 (Nov 10 2002)
=====================
 o ported to Gtk2/GNOME2

GtkTetcolor 0.5.2   (Mar 4 2002)
=================
 o source code was cleaned, possible memory leaks on old Gnome were fixed
 
GtkTetcolor 0.5.1   (Dec 6 2001)
=================
 o delay before cell destroying is now configurable
 o score label is now displayed in various colors when current score lays in top ten
 o bugfixes

GtkTetcolor 0.5.0   (Apr 9 2001)
=================
 o sound support for GNOME version
 o scores saving done using GNOME routines, non-compatible with previous versions
 o minor bugfixes

GtkTetcolor 0.4.3   (Aug 23 2000)
=================
 o fixed problem with visualization of left margin
 o French translation

GtkTetcolor 0.4.2   (Aug 16 2000)
=================
 o timer 
 o dialogs were gnomified (for GNOME version)
 o bugfixes

GtkTetcolor 0.4.1   (Aug 11 2000)
=================
 o Font selection for labels 

GtkTetcolor 0.4.0   (Aug 4 2000)
=================
 o GNOME support (optional)
 o changed formula for bonus points

GtkTetcolor 0.3.1   (Mar 28 2000)
=================
 o Bug with long players names (more than 255 characters) fixed 
 
GtkTetcolor 0.3     (Jan 27 2000)
===============
 o Removing of cells is slightly animated
 o Made it possible to switch between numeric keypad and arrows keys
 o Code cleanup

